subject: Re: [junit] Re: Thinking of improving the auto generation of test cases
msgSnippet: ... It would sure be interesting. I m not at all convinced that it would be *helpful*, though. Cheers, Ilja
messageBody:
Bob Runstein schrieb:
> How about considering a project where you generate the unit tests by
> hand and then auto generate the production code from them? Now that

It would sure be interesting. I'm not at all convinced that it would be
*helpful*, though.

Cheers, Ilja
